---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { CONTACT, withBase } from '../config/site';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Submissions"
  description="Researcher submission guidelines, acceptance criteria, and evaluation flow for Del Security's private program."
  canonicalPath="/submissions"
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold">Researcher Submissions</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-text-soft">
      We operate a private submission and evaluation program. Submissions are reviewed for reproducibility, impact, and responsible coordination readiness.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 grid gap-5">
    <article class="card p-6">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">How to submit</h2>
      <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-text-soft">
        <li>Target and affected version details</li>
        <li>Minimum reproduction checklist with exact steps</li>
        <li>Environment assumptions and prerequisites</li>
        <li>Observed impact and security relevance</li>
        <li>Evidence artifacts: logs, screenshots, trace output, or PoC notes</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-text-soft">
        Submit via <a class="text-brand underline" href={`mailto:${CONTACT.securityEmail}`}>{CONTACT.securityEmail}</a>. For sensitive content, encrypt using the <a class="text-brand underline" href={withBase('/pgp.txt')}>PGP public key</a>.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="card p-6">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">What we accept / don&apos;t accept</h2>
      <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-bg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold">We accept</h3>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1.5 pl-5 text-sm text-text-soft">
            <li>Authorized and lawful research context</li>
            <li>Technically reproducible findings</li>
            <li>Clear impact articulation and affected scope</li>
            <li>Good-faith coordination intent</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-bg p-4">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold">We decline</h3>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1.5 pl-5 text-sm text-text-soft">
            <li>Unauthorized access or intrusive activity requests</li>
            <li>Stolen data submissions or provenance gaps</li>
            <li>Low-quality claims without reproducible evidence</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article id="spec-sheet" class="card p-6">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">Submission spec sheet format</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-text-soft">
        Use this structure to improve triage speed and reproducibility. Plain text or Markdown is preferred.
      </p>
      <pre class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-line bg-bg p-4 text-xs leading-6 text-text-soft"><code>Title:
Vulnerability class:
Target / product:
Affected versions:
Tested environment:
Prerequisites:
Reproduction steps:
Expected result:
Observed result:
Impact summary:
Artifacts (logs/screenshots/PoC):
Researcher contact:
</code></pre>
    </article>

    <article class="card p-6">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">Evaluation flow</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-text-soft">
        Triage -&gt; validation -&gt; vendor-ready report -&gt; coordination. We provide status milestones throughout active review.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="card p-6">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">Compensation</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-text-soft">
        Compensation decisions are case-by-case. No fixed amounts are guaranteed. Typical factors include impact, novelty, reproducibility, and affected versions.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="card p-6">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">Discreet submissions</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-text-soft">
        We can receive discreet submissions and maintain confidential communication channels when sensitive coordination is required.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="card p-6">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">PGP quick guide</h2>
      <ol class="mt-3 list-decimal space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-text-soft">
        <li>Download our public key from <a class="text-brand underline" href={withBase('/pgp.txt')}>/pgp.txt</a>.</li>
        <li>Encrypt your submission package and include your contact details.</li>
        <li>Send encrypted content to <a class="text-brand underline" href={`mailto:${CONTACT.securityEmail}`}>{CONTACT.securityEmail}</a>.</li>
      </ol>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
